Package: RHISEA
Type: Package
Title: R Implementation of HISEA for Mixed Stock Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Sosthene", "Akia", email = "sosthene.akia@dfo-mpo.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alex", "Hanke", email = "alex.hanke@dfo-mpo.ca", role = "aut"))
Description: R implementation of the HISEA method for mixed stock analysis, 
    supporting multiple classifiers (LDA, RF, MCLUST, etc.) and estimators 
    (COOK, EM, ML). Includes simulation, bootstrap, and full analysis routines.
